Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.11,0:00:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Extra! Extra! Read all about it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.64,0:00:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry Potter, the boy who beat\NVoldemort now says he's back?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.00,0:00:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Daily Prophet!\NGet your Daily Prophet here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.57,0:00:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry Potter vs. Voldemort, round two!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.01,0:00:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister of magic Cornelius Fudge\Nmakes a statement!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.29,0:00:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard these Voldemort-rumors\Nand I for once simply don't believe it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Voldemort talks about it on his new\N"Floo-Tube" channel!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.93,0:00:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna find Harry Potter and\NI'm gonna [peep] to his [peep]!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.97,0:00:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Also there's a review on: 17 again.\N[A movie with Zac Efron]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it a little slow at the beginning,\Nbut hey...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Zac Efron,  Zefron, enough said.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.83,0:00:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen these so called "Posts",
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I still don't believe it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.95,0:01:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a ruse! You've all\Nbeen hoodwinked!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.20,0:01:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Quirrell confesses the murder\Nof Hogwarts student Cedric Diggory!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.71,0:01:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Receives life in Azkaban!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.30,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Extra! Extra! Read all about it! Extra!...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.37,0:01:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This totally sucks, man!...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is horrible!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.50,0:01:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. I mean...\NLook at this it's... it's terrible.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.89,0:01:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry Potter vs. Voldemort,\Nthe fight of the century...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.26,0:01:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not THAT! It's Hermione.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.67,0:01:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.92,0:01:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get her out of my head
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.26,0:01:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and every time I look at her\NI have these pains in my chest
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.71,0:01:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just know it's her fault,\Nthat bitch...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just not cut out for this, Harry.\NI'm not!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.46,0:02:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah man, I know what you mean.\NIt's like when you try to save the world\Nand the whole world is just against you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.47,0:02:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.33,0:02:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't about you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.96,0:02:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does every conversation we have\Nto have , have to turn into a Potter-talk?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.12,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Potter-talk...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.96,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No, I'm miserable!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.15,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And all you can do, is talk about yourself!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like the most self observed\Nguy I know!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.82,0:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you where miserable, I'd be there\Nfor you, but you won't even listen\Nto me, and I'm sick of it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.16,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So...so...so good luck with whatever\Nyou were talking about,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.03,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hope that you and Voldemort\Nlive happily ever after.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.40,0:02:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,ME, I'm never going to be happy again!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.39,0:02:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm just gonna go curl up in my\Nsock drawer and sleep for days!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.88,0:02:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.78,0:02:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you just talking to Ron?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Iwas trying to\Ntell him about Voldemort...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Would he say anything about me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...Yeah,...he said - ah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.01,0:03:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was one of them an apology for\Nhow he treated me at the Yule-Ball?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.97,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard about that. Listen,\NI was wondering, if you heard about\Nlittle something
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.42,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember: Voldemort is back,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.31,0:03:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Cedric Diggory is dead,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Quirrell is crazy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I have to save the world!\NDid you hear that, Hermione?!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.51,0:03:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually I have heard those things,\NHarry, about a thousand times.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.31,0:03:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But never have they been told\Nto me with so much sets!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.23,0:03:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Love the attitude, Harry Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting like Garfield on a Monday!\N[James A. Garfield died on a Monday after\Nhe was shot some time before]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think I have a right\Nto be a little stressed out?!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... No! No, I don't!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, this is just like\Nwith the dragon, okay?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.18,0:03:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I stressed out, I told you to prepare\Nand jet you didn't do anything\Nand you were fine!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you just played\Na little guitar!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.33,0:03:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't know what\Nyou're crying about, Harry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.59,0:03:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just like when you defeated\NVoldemort and you were a baby!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermione, come on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.31,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the friend that's supposed to\Ntell me to go to the library and\Ntrying figure that stuff out...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what, Harry?\NI don't do that anymore!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Read it and weep, Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard Voldemort's back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.06,0:04:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's trying to kill you, what do\Nyou think of that, MOON SHOES?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.90,0:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Malfoy, I unsucceded, I don't see why\Nyou're so happy about this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If Voldemort is back- which he is -
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you might so kiss Hogwarts goodbye.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You might so kiss the whole\Nplanet goodbye!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss the planet goodbye?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Having second thoughts about\NPigfarts, are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Malfoy, you're the last person\NI wanna talk to right now, okay?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.38,0:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.15,0:04:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as you're out of the way,\NI'll be the coolest kid in school!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Malfoy, that will never happen.\NEverybody hates you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, okay! This coming\Nfrom Hermione "Stranger"!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right, Malfoy!\NShe's cooler then you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, even Moaning Myrtle\Nis cooler then you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! Expelliarmus!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet! Be quiet!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.78,0:04:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.10,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What the devil is going on hereeeeee?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.22,0:05:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Draco Malfoy, pull those\Ntrousers up at once!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.13,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, I just...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.40,0:05:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it!\NI want to see you in my office!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,NOW!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault, Potter.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.49,0:05:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this! YOU'LL PAY...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice - you're the man!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me feel better!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.55,0:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Ginny, what's... I hope you've\Nsomething to say about Voldemort!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.02,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(sigh) whatever...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.... Harry?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.22,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.05,0:05:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So...We kissed at the Yule-Ball,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.76,0:06:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and...well, I thought we were\Ngonna be together forever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.48,0:06:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeeaah... that, ah...\Nthat pretty much sums it up...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginny, THIS is what's going on,\Ndon't you get it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is who... is in danger,\Nwho's near to me. We can't be\Ntogether,because...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,when Voldemort is back - which he is -
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.22,0:06:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you're in mortal peril, don't you get it?\NIt's like the Spiderman movie haven't\Nyou seen that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,MJ and Peter Parker can't  be together.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.44,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But the whole point of Spiderman two was\Nthat MJ und Peter Parker could be together\Nin the end!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.43,0:06:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know, but the point of Spiderman\Nthree is everything sucks and it falls to shit!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginny, what I'm trying to say is,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.87,0:06:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want my life to be like Spiderman\Nthree, I hated that movie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.09,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, it's just...\Nthat's my little way of saying, well
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't be together.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ginny.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such an idiot!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a... I need a Butterbeer...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Pst! Potter...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.69,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dumbledore!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen Harry, I've got some very\Nimportant things, I got to tell you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, about Voldemort?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Things that are absolutely crucial\Nfor you to know, but I can't get into it\Nright now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.36,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to meet me in my inner office\Nat ten o'clock. And come by yourself!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.94,0:07:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring that...ah - invisibility-cloak of yours\Nand don't go blabbing your mouth about this\Nto anyone else!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.60,0:07:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Voldemort has spies that could be anywhere,\Neven inside of Hogwarts!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on the only person you can trust,\NHarry, is me and Severus Snape.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen Dumbledore, I know you\Ndon't wanna hear this,...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am not so sure about...\NSnape...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, no, I'm pretty sure,\Nhe's working for Voldemort...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.57,0:07:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!? That's stupid! YOU're stupid!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.38,0:08:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! I'm positive, that night in the\Ngraveyard some Deatheater cuts\Noff his hand,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.02,0:08:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and Snape...[???]...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.42,0:08:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh ...[???]... Snape has assured me that\Nhe lost his hand in an entirely unrelated\Nincident.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.97,0:08:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbledore, why do you trust\NSnape so much?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I love him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.92,0:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, I...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet! I don't want to hear anything\Nelse about it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.59,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way, that Severus Snape is, was\Nor ever shall be a servant of Voldemort!
